outputType.name: Resource Creation Executable Output
outputType.outputPrefix: "(if not exist "${ProjName}_manifest.mrc" ((echo Manifest resource creation at %TIME% on %DATE% > "${ProjName}_manifest.mrc") & (if not exist "${ProjName}_manifest.rc" echo 1 /* CREATEPROCESS_MANIFEST_RESOURCE_ID */ 24 /* RT_MANIFEST */ ${EmbedManifest} >"${ProjName}_manifest.rc") & (if not exist "${EmbedManifest}" echo ^<?xml version^='1.0' encoding^='UTF-8' standalone^='yes'?^>^<assembly xmlns^='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:asm.v1' manifestVersion^='1.0'^>^</assembly^> >"${EmbedManifest}") & (if not exist "${EmbedResource}" (rc /fo "${EmbedResource}" ${ProjName}_manifest.rc)) & (if exist "${ProjName}_manifest.rc" del "${ProjName}_manifest.rc"))) & (echo.) & (EXIT /B 0)"

outputType.name: Resource Creation Shared Library Output
outputType.outputPrefix: "(if not exist "${ProjName}_manifest.mrc" ((echo Manifest resource creation at %TIME% on %DATE% > "${ProjName}_manifest.mrc") & (if not exist "${ProjName}_manifest.rc" echo 2 /* ISOLATIONAWARE_MANIFEST_RESOURCE_ID */ 24 /* RT_MANIFEST */ "${EmbedManifest}" >"${ProjName}_manifest.rc") & (if not exist "${EmbedManifest}" echo ^<?xml version^='1.0' encoding^='UTF-8' standalone^='yes'?^>^<assembly xmlns^='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:asm.v1' manifestVersion='1.0'^>^</assembly^> >"${EmbedManifest}") & (if not exist "${EmbedResource}" (rc /fo "${EmbedResource}" ${ProjName}_manifest.rc)) & (if exist "${ProjName}_manifest.rc" del "${ProjName}_manifest.rc"))) & (echo.) & (EXIT /B 0)"
